{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_018va2KV9ubcAFzNxUgmug9a","type":"tool_result","content":"  4860→\n  4861→| Priority | Action | Owner |\n  4862→|----------|--------|-------|\n  4863→| P0 | **Kill the Ralph process immediately.** The sprint is done. Every additional session burns tokens for zero value. | User |\n  4864→| P0 | **Add monotonic status guard to state writer.** If a story is `done` and has a proof document, reject any write that would revert it to an earlier status. | Next sprint |\n  4865→| P1 | **Add sprint-complete lock.** When done count equals total count, lock `sprint-state.json` against further writes from Ralph. | Next sprint |\n  4866→| P1 | **Add auto-termination to Ralph.** When Ralph detects 0 actionable stories, it should self-terminate instead of continuing to poll and overwrite. | Next sprint |\n  4867→| P2 | **Audit total waste from corruption sessions.** Run precise cost attribution for sessions 17-44 to quantify exact dollar waste. | Next sprint |\n  4868→\n  4869→**Session 44 is the 14th consecutive no-op session and the 28th state corruption fix. The sprint has been done for 14 sessions. KILL RALPH.**\n  4870→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01N6ikZSdbUEDmDJdZgy6Wee","session_id":"1d78ac7a-2e69-4598-8711-ac6f7cc0725e","uuid":"495436ee-d40d-4503-bc10-52059bbb47db","timestamp":"2026-03-27T16:27:07.592Z"}
